# Python LangGraph Conventions

- Keep node functions pure and deterministic over `GraphState`.
- Use pydantic models for structured outputs across node boundaries.
- Prefer explicit conditional routers over implicit branching in node internals.
- Prevent unbounded loops with retry counters and human handoff paths.
